# Setup screen configuration

# Some software (probably XWayland) does not accept negative coordinates.
# Therefore the main display is placed at high coordinates, so other
# displays can be placed in any direction.

# Get the screen output with `swaymsg -t get_outputs`
#output "LG Electronics LG HDR 4K 0x0000E7ED" mode 4096x2160@60Hz scale 2 pos 10000 10000
